These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, engineer
1. the security-guard is in an even position##4
2. the engineer is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | drawing | writing |
| Job     | engineer    | security-guard   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk        |
| Sport      | parkour  | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, salsa
There are 2 different nationalities: french, spanish
1. the french is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | metal |
| Nationality   | french | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
There 2 different types of food: grapes, lime
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person eating lime is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | milk      | tea |
| Food       | grapes | lime    |

 #################################

 
